parameters:
Chieftain "Hohoho! You've finally decided to get off your heavy backside,
eh?"
Kru "Yes... I thought it was about time to face it properly."
Chieftain "I've been waiting for this moment. Now, let me explain."
Villager "Chieftain!"
Chieftain "What's the rush?"
Villager "Just come! Please come to the village entrance!"
Chieftain "Hmm, alright, calm down."
Kru "What on earth could it be?"

Chief: "Kru, I apologize for yesterday. You went out of your way to
come..."

Kru: "It's no problem. Please don't worry about it. What did you discuss
with Banka?"

Chief: "Well, it seems he is reflecting on his actions, and we've decided
to let him stay in the village."

Chief: "The villagers are still distrustful of Banka, so we've agreed that
he should take his time to regain their trust."
Kru: "I see. Well, everyone is safe, so let's let bygones be bygones."
バンカ9
Banka: "Kru-san... thank you."
Kru: "No, you don't need to thank me... it feels weird."
バンカ8

Banka: "No, I heard from my father. About everything you've done for the
village... I can't thank you enough..."

Kru: "Well, if that's the case... From now on, let's both do our best for
the village."
バンカ4
Banka: "Yes!"

Chief: "So then. To become the chief of this village, one must pass through
three trials and be acknowledged by Lord Kuseshirei."
Kru: "Three trials?"

Chief: "That's right. You must go to the three dungeons associated with
Lord Kuseshirei, bring back the jewels, and fulfill the contract to
officially become the chief."
Kru: "I see... Understood, let's go."
Chief: "And I want you to take Banka with you as your attendant."
Kru: "Take Banka with me?"

Chief: "Yes. For his atonement and training, I want him to accompany you on
your journey."
バンカ2

Banka: "Kru-san! Please! I want to start over with a new heart! Let me work
under you! I won't be a burden!"
Kru: "But... is that really necessary...?"
バンカ6
Banka: "I'll carry your luggage or anything! Please!"

Chief: "I'm asking you as well. If he's not useful, feel free to leave him
behind."

Kru: "...Yes, I understand. It's a request from the chief himself, after
all."
バンカ5
Banka: "Kru-san! Thank you!"
Chief: "Kru, I am indebted to you. Now, depart at once!"
Kru: "Yes!"
Chieftain: "You've had a long journey. It seems it's finally over."
Kru: "Yes. I've safely retrieved the jewel."

Chieftain: "Understood. Then you should take a short rest before you go on
the next trial."
Kru: "I will do just that."
showHpGauge
"ウミを探す"

Chieftain: "Well then, it's about time to head to the cave for the next
trial."
Kru: "Yes, understood."

Chieftain: "During the previous journey, our Banka did a good job, didn't
he?"
Kru: "Yes. It was a great help when Umi fell ill."

Chieftain: "Is that so? Then, would you take him along on this journey as
well?"
Kru: "I'll be counting on him."
Chieftain: "It seems everything went well this time too."

Kru: "Yes. Everything was fine except for Umi's health deteriorating
again."
Chieftain: "Kru..."
Kru: "Chieftain?"
Chieftain: "No... it's nothing..."
Kru: "Then I'll go home and rest."
showHpGauge
"ウミを探す"
